snippet.title: Bounty Arms Teaser Trailer HD
snippet.description:
Bounty Arms Teaser Trailer Demo for UDK. Now a standalone installer.

Download the demo at Epic's UDK Showcase Page:
http://www.udk.com/showcase-bounty-arms

Bounty Arms is now available for iOS and Android. Watch the trailer here:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P7Zc76TYShQ

iOS - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bounty-arms/id592322930?mt=8

Android - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kerosenegames.ba
